children: A tender ballad about being unable to resist falling in love, “Can’t Help Falling in Love” is one of Elvis' most famous and romantic songs. Originally recorded to tie along with his movie,
, the song has since been covered by various other artists, from
as the 5th best Elvis song of all time, and it was also
ranked as the 50th most popular wedding song
